Workers have the ability to improve terrain tiles. See the help on \
Terrain and Terrain Alterations for the effects of their actions.\
"), _("\
Workers can build airbases and buoys, which Settlers cannot. \
Workers must be on board a ship to build buoys.\
")

[unit_engineers]
name          = _("Engineers")
class         = "Land"
reqs          =
  { "type", "name", "range"
    "Tech", "Explosives", "Player"
  }
