legend = _("The Avars or Eurasian Avars were an ancient nomadic\
 confederation of mixed origin. The dominant language of this group was\
 presumably Proto-Bulgarian within the Turkic Oghuz language subgroup,\
 but the true origin of the Avars is unknown. It is possible they were\
 originally a Rouran or Hephthalite group. After settling in Pannonia they\
 subjugated the local Slavic tribes. Gradually they lost power and\
 political importance and eventually the Avars blended with Slavic peoples.")

